pageProduct.name: VitalStrength Pre Workout Shot Watermelon Smash 5 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

VItalstrength Pre Workout Shot. Take Pre-Workout Gel Shots prior to training to increase motivation, boost energy & endurance.

On-the-go Pre-Workout Gel. No water or mixing just a convenient shot of energy & focus. Vital Strength's Pre-Workout shots feature an innovative design that means you can take them anywhere, anytime. Easy to use & specially formulated to increase energy, focus & strength.

Our concentrated formula is loaded with nitric oxide boosters, L-citrulline and Beta-alanine for increased energy production, muscle strength, power & endurance. Carefully selected stimulants give you intense pumps pushing you to train harder, for longer. Convenient & easy to transport these Pre-Workout shots are perfect for any occasion.

•  Convenient easy to use gel shot, consumer anywhere anytime
•  No water or mixing required.
•  1.5g Nitric Oxide AAKG increased blood flow to muscle & tissues
•  1g Beta Alanine to aid muscular endurance
•  2.5g L-Citrulline boosts blood flow
•  200mg of caffeine for explosive energy
•  860mg Taurine enhances athletic capacity
•  Improves physical performance
•  Delays mental fatigue
•  Promotes clarity throughout entire workout

Size: 5 Pack

Flavour: Watermelon Smash

Serving Size: 10g

Servings Per Pack: 5

Warnings

THIS PRODUCT SHOULD BE USED IN CONJUNCTION WITH AN APPROPRIATE PHYSICAL TRAINING OR EXERCISE PROGRAM. THIS PRODUCT IS NOT A SOLE SOURCE OF NUTRITION AND SHOULD BE CONSUMED IN CONJUNCTION WITH A NUTRITIOUS DIET AND APPROPRIATE FLUID INTAKE. NOT SUITABLE FOR CHILDREN UNDER 15 YEARS OR PREGNANT WOMEN. SHOULD ONLY BE USED UNDER MEDICAL OR DIETETIC SUPERVISION. EXCEEDING THE RECOMMENDED SERVING SIZE MAY CAUSE HARM DUE TO THE HIGH LEVELS CAFFEINE AND OTHER NUTRIENTS. CONTAINS CAFFEINE: NOT RECOMMENDED FOR CHILDREN, PREGNANT OR LACTATING WOMEN INDIVIDUALS SENSITIVE TO CAFFEINE.

Ingredients

L-Arginine AKG, Beta Alanine, L-Citrullene, Taurine, Caffeine, L-Tyrosine, Glucuronolactone, Folic Acid, Magnesium Citrate, Zinc (Gluconate), Vitamin B12, Vit B3, Vit B6, Vit B5, Vit B9 (Folate), Vit C, Zinc (Gluconate), Maltodextrin, Citric acid, Flavours, Ascorbic acid, Carboxylmethylcellulose, Silicon dioxide, Sucralose, Acesulphame Potassium, Colour, Guar Gum, Xanthan Gum, Potassium Sorbate, Water. Soy Lecithin.

Contains: Contains: Soy.

Allergen Contains: Soy

Directions

Consume 1 shot to assess tolerance, progress to 2 shots if required. Do not exceed two shots per day.
